{"tid":1714894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［核爆］藍絲慶祝緊利君雅被炒，求FC","createTime":"2019-11-13T03:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T01:20:56.000Z","uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fbacac7f180cee078678629012cd0e2ce3f33674","tid":1714894,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3FVuaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3FVuaR.jpg&h=4cf42c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咩料啊，屌佢老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e35e28f9f2f4d8385e0fd01e2d91d282232d2a","tid":1714894,"uid":31773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"尋晚先做完live<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7877fb2081e150438a5f60dde758e4ca61a9ac4b","tid":1714894,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=8728